 wang and developed by an independent disk manufacturer shugart associates  taylor michael  how emotional tagging can push leaders to make bad decisions • iveybusinessjournalcom retrieved    the intel  processor is a slightly modified version of the earlier  its external data bus is  bits wide as compared to the s  thus requiring two bus cycles to transfer a bit value this resulted in slower execution time for some instructions  this may be where the designers of wordperfect got the idea of stickers with altctrlshift colors for the fkeys  library home page — georgetown law llgeorgetownedu retrieved    a b cbsi findarticlescom retrieved  permanent dead link  archived copy archived from the original on august   retrieved may     clevel refers to chief level officers in an organization  assume  clevel officers per fortune  organization market size is  units assume  ordinary clerical workers in the same organization market size is  units  cunningham resigns as wang president latimes   a b c history of wang laboratories inc – fundinguniverse fundinguniversecom retrieved    stein charles  a hightech david faltered as goliath the boston globe november   business section p  if you could attach the kitchen sink they would announce that too   company news wang laboratories emerges from bankruptcy new york times september   retrieved august     company news wang headquarters auctioned for  new york times associated press february   retrieved august     wang towers team shifts focus onto development boston business journal august   retrieved march     getronics and transvirtual systems deliver getronics’ next generation of wang®vs™ computer systems pdf transvirtualsystemscom retrieved    getronics announces end of support for legacy getronics wang® vs™ systems pdf transvirtualsystemscom retrieved    kpns getronics enters partnership with compucom sells north american ops forbes june     hack gostl july   re vgsx ongoing support pdf transvirtual systems retrieved august    exter