es in  and focused on investments in infrastructure and clean technology prior to this he served as a partner of spectrum equity investors now spectrum equity management lp where he led investments in next generation communications companies networking companies emerging communication service and infrastructure providers he served as a vice president of business development at mindscape making investments in acquisitions of online and software companies he invests in venture and growth orientedcompanies with a focus on the information technology space prior to mindscape he developed market and technology strategies at the boston consulting group inc and worked with clients such as pacific gas  electric electric power research institute att pacific bell apple computer wiltel att lucent philips and siemens he also worked as a director at pacific bells new technology group evaluating new technologies and service opportunities mr wang started his career as a software engineer and product manager at intuit inc he serves as a director at tricn inc eci telecom dnd inc aryaka networks inc he has been director at threatmetrix inc since june   he has been a director at harvestai since march   he has been a director of cyphort inc since october   and digital shadows ltd since february   he has been a director of avaak inc western association of venture capitalists and ibm cloud video inc since march   he served as director of trustid inc since may  mr wang serves as a member of advisory board at leader ventures he served as a director of trendium inc exalt communications inc now exalt wireless inc the cloudscaling group inc and netcordia inc he served as a director of scalearc inc until may   he served as a director of sevcon inc from february   to march   he served as a director of orative corporation cygent inc ankeena networks inc vocaldata inc nokeena networks inc speedera networks inc sevenspace inc netrake corporation clarus systems inc he served as the chairman of the board at sevcon inc since december  until february   mr wang holds an mba degree with distinction from harvard university an ms degree in industrial engineering and a bs degree with honors in electrical engineering from stanford university he holds a bsc in applied mathematics from brown university and a masters degree in public administration from the john f kennedy school of governmentread full background corporate headquarters   united statesphone fax  board members memberships directoreci telecom dnd incdirectortricn incvice president comarketing chair and directorwestern association of venture capitalistsdirectoravaak incdirectoraryaka networks incpresentdirectoribm cloud video incpresentdirectorcyphort incpresentdirectorharvestaipresentdirectordigital shadows ltdpresentdirectorthreatmetrix inc education ms stanford universitybs stanford universitymba harvard business schoolbs brown universitymasters degree john f kennedy school of government other affiliations intuit incspectrum equity management lptrinity venturescygent inctrendium incspeedera networks inceci telecom dnd incvocaldata incthe boston consulting group incstanford universitysevcon incnetrake corporationsevenspace incharvard business schooltricn inctrinity vii lpbrown universityjohn f kennedy school of governmentorative corporationclarus systems llcnetcordia incleader venturesexalt wireless incthreatmetrix incibm cloud video incankeena networks incavaak inctrinity x lptrustid incaryaka networks incthe cloudscaling group inccyphort incscalearc inctrinity ventures xi lpdigital shadows ltdharvestaiasp capital annual compensation there is no annual compensation data available stocks options there is no stock options data available total compensation there is no total compensation data available request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for